metadata.name: INDVR Brands Inc
metadata.description: INDVR Brands Inc. provides personnel and management resources, and infrastructure and equipment for use in production, cultivation, and dispensary operations of licensed cannabis businesses in the United States. It also offers marketing and payroll administration, subleases facilities, and subleases equipment services. The company markets its products under the Cannabis, The Joint, Incognito by Cannabis, Fire by Cannabis, Cannabis Prime, Fat Face Farms, Honu, and INDVR names. The company was formerly known as Cannabis One Holdings Inc. and changed its name to INDVR Brands Inc. in August 2020. INDVR Brands Inc. is headquartered in Calgary, Canada.
